data.text: What a beautiful way to encourage & set a great example of #YouComeFirst.

GO FIRST salutes the quick actions of its crew. Via a video conference call, Mr. Kaushik Khona - CEO & other senior members of GO FIRST joined the passenger & the doctor in a felicitation ceremony to present mementos to the crew.

data.text: Working together as a team, the doctor & a crew member performed CPR and used the AED to help the passenger recover from this life-threatening emergency. It was indeed a flight of angels - the crew & doctor that saved the life of the passenger!

Our crew members #Abhishek , #Shilpa , #Sumeet & #Imlitemsula were quick to respond & rushed to the aid of the passenger. From the rigorous training that the crew receive, they were quick to calm fellow passengers & identify a doctor on board. https://t.co/R9BGEkqSZ9

'The prompt action by the cabin crew & doctor on flight G8-057 helped save the life of the passenger'.

On May 8th, 2022, a passenger suffered a cardiac arrest while travelling from #Kannur to #Dubai & needed immediate medical attention. https://t.co/T2YvuFRfqt

urls.title: Food & Beverage (Menu) - Go First
urls.description: Satisfy those cravings in-flight, by simply pre-booking your favourite snacks online or choose from our onboard refreshed menu. You can pick from an array of veg, non-veg, and Jain snacks to please your taste buds. Go First accepts credit/debit card payments on all domestic and international flights for on-board meal purchases. Please note that Diners Club and Amex cards are not accepted. Cash transactions are not applicable on international flights. Go First has added Raj Uphaar’s Raj Amrut rice chakri,
